descriptions:
["DescriptionGulf Sotheby's International Realty is proud to offer this exclusive and sophisticated 3 bedroom apartment in DT1 - Downtown Dubai, by the Award-winning Boutique developer, Ellington Properties. Each Ellington development stands out for its superior design, enhanced features, and lifestyle within the community, representing one of the most unique and compelling options for both investors and end-users. 
Main Features: 
. Heightened 3.2m ceilings in living room and bedrooms; 
. Premium tile flooring in Entry, Living, Dining, Master Bedroom, and Guest Bedroom;
. Expansive and elegantly proportioned window-walls with Downtown city views;
. Generous outside living balcony areas. Bespoke crafted and fitted wardrobes for walk-in closets and dressing rooms;
. Professional-standard appliances from Miele;
. Ellington's signature fragrance in the Lobby;
. Free Wi-Fi in common areas;
. Amenities include Swimming Pool & Lap Pool, Barbecue Area, Gym & Changing Room, Retail Area, Public Art Gallery. 
Location:
. 2 min from Dubai Mall and Burj Khalifa. 
. Under 8 minutes to Dubai Int. Financial Center. 
. 15 min from Dubai International Airport. 
. 20 min from Burj Al Arab, Jumeirah. 
Exquisite and unique, DT1 is an edgy and slick statement on the urban qualities of Downtown Dubai, and a celebration of design and art, with its own gallery. A truly beautiful boutique property developed by the Architectural firm Perkins+Will. 
Contact Gulf Sotheby's International Realty today for your private viewing of this extraordinary project."]
